&lt;h3 id="22-x-y-z-fixed-angles由-r-推算-angles"&gt;2.2 X-Y-Z Fixed Angles——由 R 推算 angles
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h1 id="endbmatrix"&gt;$$
\prescript{A}{B}{R}_{XYZ}(\gamma, \beta, \alpha) =
\begin{bmatrix}
