s\alpha c\beta &amp;amp; s\alpha s\beta s\gamma + c\alpha c\gamma &amp;amp; s\alpha s\beta c\gamma - c\alpha s\gamma \
-s\beta &amp;amp; c\beta s\gamma &amp;amp; c\beta c\gamma
